== Opening #{{<font color=red><b>}} Opening {{</b></font>}} 
I am actively looking for self-motivated Ph.D. students in the fields of Control, Aerospace Systems, Robotics, and Machine Learning, with starting dates in either Spring or Fall 2024. Applicants should have a bachelor's or master's degree in Aerospace Engineering, Mechanical Engineering, Electrical Engineering, or a related discipline. Ideal candidates will have a solid foundation in one or more areas of control theory, machine\/reinforcement learning, aerospace systems, and robotics.  To apply, please send a detailed resume/curriculum vitae, transcripts, and a short interest statement to Dr. Pan Zhao. 